Class CreateUserGUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.CreateUserGUI

  • public class CreateUserGUI
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates the UI to a create a user that will be able to access the system. The User can either be a seller or buyer. This class acts as the view/controller in the MVC relationship with the UPDatabase class and User class. This class uses the Strategy also by using the Layout managers to build the UI.
    Author:
    Joey
